description: TEHRAN – Iran national team defeated India 10-0 on Friday to remain top of the 2024 IIHF Women's Asia and Oceania Cup standing table.
title: Iran one step away from 2024 IIHF Women's Asia and Oceania Cup gold medal

description: MADRID- The leaders of Hamas and Islamic Jihad visited Tehran this past Wednesday, March 26th, to hold various meetings with the authorities of the Islamic Republic.
title: The Meaningful Visit of Palestinian Resistance Leaders to Iran

description: Hezbollah has carried out multiple strikes against Israeli settlements and positions in the northern sector of the 1948 Israeli-occupied territories, as part of another round of retaliatory operations amid the Gaza war.
title: Lebanon’s Hezbollah hits Israeli positions

description: A British charity has launched a nationwide billboard campaign calling on the UK government to end its arms sales and trade agreements with Israel if it continues its bombardment of Gaza.
title: UK charity calls for end to arms trade with Israel

description: At least 71 more Palestinians were killed and 112 others injured over the last 24 hours, as Israel continues its onslaught on the besieged Gaza Strip, the territory’s Health Ministry said on Friday, Anadolu Agency reports.
title: Israel’s genocidal war in Gaza continues as death toll climbs to 32,623

description: Palestine’s Ministry of Foreign Affairs welcomes the new ICJ provisions, saying they challenge “Israel’s historic rebellion against international law”.
title: Palestinian foreign ministry says credibility at stake after new ICJ provisions

description: Syria condemned the terrorist aggression launched by the Israeli occupation entity at dawn Friday, targeting a number of points in Aleppo countryside, Sana news agency reported.
title: Syria condemns Israeli "terrorist aggression" on Aleppo countryside

description: TEHRAN –Iranian voice actor Ali-Asghar Rezainik died of heart failure at his home in Tehran on Wednesday. He was 67.
title: Voice actor Ali-Asghar Rezainik passes away

description: TEHRAN- “A Band of Dreamers and a Judge” by Iranian director Hesam Eslami will go on screen at the Hot Docs, a major Canadian international documentary festival, which is scheduled to be held from April 25 to May 5.
title: Iranian documentary to go on screen at Hot Docs

description: TEHRAN-The 1st Abbas Kiarostami International Short Film Festival, a platform dedicated to honoring the role and impact of Kiarostami in the history of cinema, has called for entries.
title: 1st Abbas Kiarostami International Short Film Festival calls for entries

description: TEHRAN-Italo Calvino’s book about his trip to Iran five decades ago has been released in the bookstores across the country.
title: Italo Calvino’s book on Iran published in Persian

description: TEHRAN - The Forests, Rangelands, and Watershed Management Organization is making efforts to protect ecosystems across the country, Abbas-Ali Nobakht, head of the FRWMO, has said.
title: Watershed management attempts to protect ecosystems: official

description: TEHRAN -The Iranian Red Crescent Society (IRCS) and Tehran Fire Department have been assessed by the International Search and Rescue Advisory Group (INSARAG) and Emergency Situations and Elimination of Consequences of Natural Disasters of the Russian Federation (EMERCOM).
title: INSARAG, Russian EMERCOM assess Iranian crisis management teams

description: TEHRAN – More than 250 people have voluntarily participated in a program to save Asiatic cheetahs that are usually killed in road accidents in the northeast of the country.
title: Public participation slashes cheetah road fatality to zero

description: HAINAN - The Boao Forum for Asia (BFA) Annual Conference 2024 started on Thursday in Boao town located next to the eastern coastal city of Qionghai in Hainan Province, in the South China Sea.
title: China's Hainan Province holds BFA annual conference

description: TEHRAN - In a recent announcement by Mohammad-Ali Shahhosseini, the Deputy for Economic and Tourism Affairs of the Yazd Governorate, Fahraj village has been designated as a target village for rural tourism.
title: Fahraj chosen as target village for rural tourism
